headline: Camden Property Trust Announces Third Quarter 2025 Dividend
summary: HOUSTON, September 15, 2025--The Board of Trust Managers of Camden Property Trust (NYSE:CPT) (the "Company") declared a third quarter cash dividend of $1.05 per share to holders of record as of September 30, 2025 of its Common Shares of Beneficial Interest. The dividend is to be paid on October 17, 2025.

headline: What Does the Recent Apartment Sale Mean for Camden’s Share Price in 2025?
summary: If you have been eyeing Camden Property Trust's stock, you are probably wondering whether now is the right time to act or if you should wait things out. The past few months have been a tug of war for the share price. While the 30-day return is up 2.5%, the year-to-date performance is still down 4.5%, and the stock has slid 9.2% over the past year.
